[
  {
    "startTime": 13.28,
    "endTime": 16.0,
    "text": "for the past 24 years i have been a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.0,
    "endTime": 19.52,
    "text": "firefighter in huntington west virginia"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.52,
    "endTime": 22.32,
    "text": "as firefighters my team and i are tasked"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.32,
    "endTime": 25.92,
    "text": "with saving lives"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.08,
    "endTime": 30.56,
    "text": "and property from such disasters as car"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.56,
    "endTime": 31.519,
    "text": "wrecks"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.519,
    "endTime": 32.96,
    "text": "house fires"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.96,
    "endTime": 34.719,
    "text": "and also life-threatening medical"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.719,
    "endTime": 37.52,
    "text": "emergencies"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.6,
    "endTime": 40.079,
    "text": "i am a woman leading a department in a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.079,
    "endTime": 42.239,
    "text": "male-dominated profession"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.239,
    "endTime": 45.12,
    "text": "and ten years ago i decided to increase"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.12,
    "endTime": 47.84,
    "text": "my medical knowledge and i received a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.84,
    "endTime": 49.6,
    "text": "nursing degree"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.6,
    "endTime": 52.16,
    "text": "that was because it became clear"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.16,
    "endTime": 54.559,
    "text": "that the next big threat facing not only"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.559,
    "endTime": 56.879,
    "text": "my city but other cities around the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.879,
    "endTime": 58.879,
    "text": "country was not the one and done"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.879,
    "endTime": 61.359,
    "text": "disaster where you can ride in like the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.359,
    "endTime": 64.799,
    "text": "calvary as a firefighter"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.799,
    "endTime": 67.04,
    "text": "put out the fire and leave feeling like"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.04,
    "endTime": 68.72,
    "text": "you have made a difference and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.72,
    "endTime": 70.56,
    "text": "everything is okay"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.56,
    "endTime": 74.479,
    "text": "the next big disaster in my city was and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.479,
    "endTime": 77.2,
    "text": "is the long debilitating"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.2,
    "endTime": 78.479,
    "text": "and lethal"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.479,
    "endTime": 82.0,
    "text": "disaster known as opioid addiction"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.0,
    "endTime": 84.4,
    "text": "we now call this a health epidemic and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.4,
    "endTime": 87.28,
    "text": "we have replaced the name addiction with"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.28,
    "endTime": 89.6,
    "text": "substance use disorder"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.6,
    "endTime": 91.759,
    "text": "to give you some perspective of how"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.759,
    "endTime": 95.2,
    "text": "significant this epidemic has become"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.2,
    "endTime": 97.36,
    "text": "in 2017"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.36,
    "endTime": 101.36,
    "text": "in my county of five thousand people"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.36,
    "endTime": 102.72,
    "text": "we saw"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.72,
    "endTime": 104.159,
    "text": "eighteen hundred and thirty one"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.159,
    "endTime": 106.079,
    "text": "overdoses"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.079,
    "endTime": 108.72,
    "text": "a hundred and eighty three deaths from"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.72,
    "endTime": 111.2,
    "text": "overdose"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.2,
    "endTime": 113.68,
    "text": "this is the job of my firefighters as"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.68,
    "endTime": 116.56,
    "text": "well as other agencies to respond to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.56,
    "endTime": 118.798,
    "text": "that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.96,
    "endTime": 121.6,
    "text": "excuse me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.24,
    "endTime": 123.68,
    "text": "so"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.68,
    "endTime": 126.079,
    "text": "watching this epidemic unfold for"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.079,
    "endTime": 127.439,
    "text": "several years"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.439,
    "endTime": 130.239,
    "text": "i developed some insight"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.239,
    "endTime": 133.04,
    "text": "for this disaster we need to redefine"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.04,
    "endTime": 135.599,
    "text": "our job as a first responder"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.599,
    "endTime": 138.319,
    "text": "we need to be more than just the calvary"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.319,
    "endTime": 141.2,
    "text": "we need to do more than just save a life"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.2,
    "endTime": 144.16,
    "text": "we need to find ways to real rebuild"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.16,
    "endTime": 145.44,
    "text": "that life"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.44,
    "endTime": 146.959,
    "text": "and it's going to take a lot of people"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.959,
    "endTime": 148.4,
    "text": "to do that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.4,
    "endTime": 150.239,
    "text": "and that is exactly what we are trying"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.239,
    "endTime": 153.68,
    "text": "to do in huntington west virginia"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.68,
    "endTime": 156.48,
    "text": "now let me give you some insight as to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.48,
    "endTime": 158.72,
    "text": "what we do"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.72,
    "endTime": 161.599,
    "text": "this is why first this is what happens"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.599,
    "endTime": 164.239,
    "text": "when somebody overdoses"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.239,
    "endTime": 166.08,
    "text": "imagine you are somebody who is"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.08,
    "endTime": 168.319,
    "text": "suffering from the brain disorder"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.319,
    "endTime": 170.4,
    "text": "of addiction"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.4,
    "endTime": 171.84,
    "text": "you are fragile"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.84,
    "endTime": 176.0,
    "text": "you're embarrassed you're ashamed"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.0,
    "endTime": 178.72,
    "text": "and you overdose"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.72,
    "endTime": 180.8,
    "text": "maybe a friend or a family member calls"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.8,
    "endTime": 182.48,
    "text": "9-1-1"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.48,
    "endTime": 184.4,
    "text": "and then all of a sudden"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.4,
    "endTime": 186.239,
    "text": "you were awakened"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.239,
    "endTime": 188.239,
    "text": "by five or six"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.239,
    "endTime": 191.36,
    "text": "strangers total strangers in uniform and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.36,
    "endTime": 193.28,
    "text": "they're rubbing your sternum and they're"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.28,
    "endTime": 196.239,
    "text": "saying wake up wake up you overdosed you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.239,
    "endTime": 197.68,
    "text": "could have died"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.68,
    "endTime": 200.4,
    "text": "now would you not be defensive and angry"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.4,
    "endTime": 202.72,
    "text": "because i know i would be"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.72,
    "endTime": 205.36,
    "text": "and on top of that those strangers gave"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.36,
    "endTime": 207.519,
    "text": "you a dose of naloxone which has sent"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.519,
    "endTime": 209.36,
    "text": "you into withdrawals"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.36,
    "endTime": 213.519,
    "text": "or what is better known as dope sickness"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.519,
    "endTime": 215.68,
    "text": "dope sickness makes you feel absolutely"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 215.68,
    "endTime": 217.04,
    "text": "horrible"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.04,
    "endTime": 220.64,
    "text": "some say it's like the flu times 10"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.64,
    "endTime": 223.68,
    "text": "nausea vomiting diarrhea"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.68,
    "endTime": 225.36,
    "text": "body aches"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.36,
    "endTime": 228.4,
    "text": "so not only did we as strangers"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 228.4,
    "endTime": 230.48,
    "text": "wake you up"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.48,
    "endTime": 232.48,
    "text": "but we also made you feel"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232.48,
    "endTime": 234.159,
    "text": "really sick"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.159,
    "endTime": 236.959,
    "text": "so in turn you the patient"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 236.959,
    "endTime": 239.36,
    "text": "are not going to be very kind to us"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.36,
    "endTime": 241.2,
    "text": "and you're going to refuse medical"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 241.2,
    "endTime": 243.68,
    "text": "treatment further medical treatment"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.68,
    "endTime": 245.84,
    "text": "okay well then that's going to frustrate"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 245.84,
    "endTime": 247.599,
    "text": "the heck out of us"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 247.599,
    "endTime": 249.92,
    "text": "and we're going to be mad because you're"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.92,
    "endTime": 254.0,
    "text": "ungrateful that we just saved your life"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.0,
    "endTime": 257.44,
    "text": "this is not a good dynamic here"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 257.44,
    "endTime": 259.68,
    "text": "so"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.0,
    "endTime": 264.16,
    "text": "what we are dealing with is a brain"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 264.16,
    "endTime": 265.44,
    "text": "disorder"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 265.44,
    "endTime": 268.32,
    "text": "that changes your thinking it convinces"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 268.32,
    "endTime": 271.36,
    "text": "you that you don't have a problem"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 271.36,
    "endTime": 272.88,
    "text": "so"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 272.88,
    "endTime": 275.52,
    "text": "this might have been not only the first"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 275.52,
    "endTime": 277.36,
    "text": "time you've overdosed it might have been"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 277.36,
    "endTime": 278.56,
    "text": "the third"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 278.56,
    "endTime": 282.08,
