  },
  {
    "startTime": 282.08,
    "endTime": 285.039,
    "text": "have revived you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 286.32,
    "endTime": 288.96,
    "text": "this is not a good situation"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 288.96,
    "endTime": 291.12,
    "text": "second"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 291.12,
    "endTime": 293.68,
    "text": "first responders do not receive much"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 293.68,
    "endTime": 296.639,
    "text": "education on what substance use disorder"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 296.639,
    "endTime": 297.6,
    "text": "is"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 297.6,
    "endTime": 300.16,
    "text": "neither does the medical community"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 300.16,
    "endTime": 303.28,
    "text": "we're not trained how to deal with those"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 303.28,
    "endTime": 306.479,
    "text": "suffering from substance use disorder"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 306.479,
    "endTime": 308.0,
    "text": "i am trained to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 308.0,
    "endTime": 310.56,
    "text": "to put out many different types of fires"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 310.56,
    "endTime": 312.56,
    "text": "i am trained to save a life in the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 312.56,
    "endTime": 315.28,
    "text": "moment but i am not trained to deal with"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 315.28,
    "endTime": 317.52,
    "text": "the intricate interaction between first"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 317.52,
    "endTime": 320.08,
    "text": "responders the healthcare community"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 320.08,
    "endTime": 322.88,
    "text": "social services and the wider community"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 322.88,
    "endTime": 325.199,
    "text": "that is necessary to save a life long"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 325.199,
    "endTime": 327.44,
    "text": "term"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 327.44,
    "endTime": 330.0,
    "text": "thirdly"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 330.16,
    "endTime": 331.52,
    "text": "and this"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 331.52,
    "endTime": 333.039,
    "text": "hits home"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 333.039,
    "endTime": 335.84,
    "text": "as a first responder i consider myself"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 335.84,
    "endTime": 337.199,
    "text": "the calvary"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 337.199,
    "endTime": 340.16,
    "text": "we want we're knights in shining armor"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 340.16,
    "endTime": 342.72,
    "text": "we want to swoop in do our job and leave"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 342.72,
    "endTime": 345.12,
    "text": "feeling satisfied that we've made a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 345.12,
    "endTime": 347.36,
    "text": "difference in somebody's life"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 347.36,
    "endTime": 349.52,
    "text": "but that just doesn't happen when we're"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 349.52,
    "endTime": 351.759,
    "text": "dealing with somebody with substance use"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 351.759,
    "endTime": 354.16,
    "text": "disorder"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 354.16,
    "endTime": 357.52,
    "text": "we leave feeling frustrated and useless"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 357.52,
    "endTime": 359.6,
    "text": "we deal with the same people over and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 359.6,
    "endTime": 363.28,
    "text": "over again with no positive outcome"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 363.28,
    "endTime": 365.36,
    "text": "and you know what at some point i"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 365.36,
    "endTime": 368.479,
    "text": "realized that it is up to us as first"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 368.479,
    "endTime": 371.28,
    "text": "responders and as a community to solve"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 371.28,
    "endTime": 374.0,
    "text": "this problem to find better ways to deal"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 374.0,
    "endTime": 377.199,
    "text": "with those that are suffering"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 377.199,
    "endTime": 378.639,
    "text": "so we so"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 378.639,
    "endTime": 380.639,
    "text": "what i did is i started"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 380.639,
    "endTime": 382.319,
    "text": "observing more"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 382.319,
    "endTime": 383.919,
    "text": "on overdoses"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 383.919,
    "endTime": 386.319,
    "text": "i started talking and listening to my"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 386.319,
    "endTime": 387.52,
    "text": "patients"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 387.52,
    "endTime": 389.36,
    "text": "i wanted to know"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 389.36,
    "endTime": 392.24,
    "text": "what led them to where they are"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 392.24,
    "endTime": 395.12,
    "text": "what exactly are they experiencing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 395.12,
    "endTime": 397.68,
    "text": "what makes their situation worse what"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 397.68,
    "endTime": 400.08,
    "text": "makes their situation better"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 400.08,
    "endTime": 403.12,
    "text": "i began experimenting with my words"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 403.12,
    "endTime": 405.68,
    "text": "and paying attention to my own actions"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 405.68,
    "endTime": 409.759,
    "text": "and how it affected those of my patients"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 409.759,
    "endTime": 411.84,
    "text": "the education"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 411.84,
    "endTime": 414.16,
    "text": "that i have received and continue to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 414.16,
    "endTime": 416.479,
    "text": "receive on a street level"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 416.479,
    "endTime": 418.0,
    "text": "in huntington"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 418.0,
    "endTime": 419.68,
    "text": "has been both eye-opening and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 419.68,
    "endTime": 422.96,
    "text": "life-changing for me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 422.96,
    "endTime": 424.24,
    "text": "so"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 424.24,
    "endTime": 426.319,
    "text": "in huntington west virginia we have come"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 426.319,
    "endTime": 428.319,
    "text": "together as a community"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 428.319,
    "endTime": 430.479,
    "text": "and we are changing the way that we"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 430.479,
    "endTime": 432.8,
    "text": "treat those that suffer from this"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 432.8,
    "endTime": 436.08,
    "text": "horrible disease"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 436.08,
    "endTime": 439.12,
    "text": "we have started many programs and it's"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 439.12,
    "endTime": 440.8,
    "text": "making a difference"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 440.8,
    "endTime": 444.4,
    "text": "i'll tell you about just a few of those"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 444.4,
    "endTime": 445.599,
    "text": "last year"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 445.599,
    "endTime": 448.88,
    "text": "we started a quick response team"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 448.88,
    "endTime": 451.44,
    "text": "qrt for short"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 451.44,
    "endTime": 454.72,
    "text": "the team consists of a paramedic"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 454.72,
    "endTime": 456.4,
    "text": "a police officer"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 456.4,
    "endTime": 458.88,
    "text": "somebody in the recovery community and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 458.88,
    "endTime": 461.52,
    "text": "somebody in the faith community"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 461.52,
    "endTime": 463.68,
    "text": "as a team they go out and visit people"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 463.68,
    "endTime": 466.56,
    "text": "who have overdosed within 72 hours of"
  },
  {
